          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1658227162783-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>couscous</strong> to a heatproof bowl with the <strong>vegetable stock</strong> and <strong>sultanas</strong>, cover with <strong>cling film</strong> and set aside until all the water has absorbed</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
